## 12. Risk Register

| # | Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation | Contingency |
|---|------|-----------|--------|------------|-------------|
| 1 | Claude misparses inventory message (wrong qty/product) | Medium | High | Confirmation card shows parsed data before DB write. User must explicitly confirm. Few-shot examples in prompt improve accuracy. | Add "Report incorrect parsing" button → logs for prompt improvement. Allow manual edit of parsed data before confirm. |
| 2 | Claude API costs unsustainable at scale | Low | High | Limit system prompt to 50 products. Cap history to 20 messages. `max_tokens: 1024`. Cache repeated queries. | Implement per-business daily message caps. Downgrade to Haiku for stock checks. Add direct-command shortcuts that bypass AI. |
| 3 | Supabase RLS misconfiguration leaking cross-tenant data | Low | Critical | Defense-in-depth: RLS + app-level `WHERE business_id`. Pre-deployment RLS test checklist. `get_user_business_ids()` function for consistency. | Immediate hotfix deploy. Audit all table policies. Notify affected users per data breach protocol. |
| 4 | Stock going negative due to race conditions | Medium | Medium | `SELECT ... FOR UPDATE` via RPC function. Reject if result < 0. | Nightly cron to flag negative stock levels and alert. Allow manual correction via adjustment. |
| 5 | User abandonment during onboarding | Medium | Medium | 3-step wizard (not 5+). Step 3 is the "aha moment" — real AI interaction. Progress indicator. Pre-filled suggestion message. | Follow-up email sequence (Day 1, 3, 7) with tips. In-app "Continue setup" banner. |
| 6 | Competitor replication | Medium | Low | Speed to market. Deep integration with African payment/messaging (WhatsApp). Community building. Brand trust. | Accelerate unique features (voice input, receipt scanning). Focus on retention over acquisition. |
| 7 | Offline sync conflicts | Low (MVP) | Medium | MVP: network-required with offline banner. No offline data mutation. | Phase 2: implement last-write-wins sync with conflict log for manual resolution. |

