## 14. Post-MVP Roadmap

| Feature | Phase | Estimate | Dependencies |
|---------|-------|----------|--------------|
| Voice input | 2 | 2 weeks | Web Speech API or Whisper API. Transcribe → pipe to existing chat pipeline. |
| WhatsApp integration | 2 | 3 weeks | WhatsApp Business API (via Twilio or Meta). Webhook receives messages → same Claude pipeline → respond via API. |
| Receipt photo scanning (OCR) | 2 | 3 weeks | Claude Vision (multimodal). Upload photo → Claude extracts line items → same confirmation card flow. |
| Barcode scanning | 2 | 2 weeks | `html5-qrcode` library. Scan → lookup product by SKU → show stock or log transaction. |
| Multi-currency support | 2 | 1 week | Add `exchange_rates` table. Convert displays based on business currency. |
| Accounting sync (QuickBooks, Wave) | 3 | 4 weeks | OAuth integration. Map Stoka transactions to journal entries. Periodic sync via cron. |
| Native mobile apps | 3 | 8 weeks | React Native or Capacitor wrapping the PWA with push notifications. |
| Public API for third-party integrations | 3 | 3 weeks | REST API with API key auth. OpenAPI spec. Rate limiting per key. |
| Offline-first with sync | 2 | 4 weeks | IndexedDB for local queue. Background sync on reconnect. Last-write-wins conflict resolution. |
| Advanced analytics (predictive) | 3 | 3 weeks | Use Claude to analyze 90-day trends and predict stockouts. Weekly AI report delivered via email. |

**Phase 2 target**: 4–6 weeks post-launch, driven by user feedback.
**Phase 3 target**: 3–4 months post-launch, driven by revenue traction.
